## Changelog
### Features
* 3558b71471e91230ca4e87c1969c9dca62cd9b54 feat: Use textconv with external diff commands
* 4cb112387262f11f4b13db7461889161015e4d7f feat: Add interactive config variable
* bddbf7f0f0ca295af2140938143b40a2af9b7690 feat: Add initial policy on LLM-generated contributions
* dac078f51cde3c7ab1be1c77446f6487d8a14bee feat: Warn about future removal of insecure hashes
* fa4e390ccc0a86e494c0bff5d6944636958df905 feat: Add .chezmoi.destDir template variable
### Fixes
* 57ee74ada4d93f5c307951190377e02036d870fc fix: Replace Expand-Archive with System.IO.Compression.ZipFile
* e038aad452ea6a335c52a5503124c3bd5aa27bb6 fix: More reliable arch detection in install.ps1
* 23de4476284bb694372eb378d4292a9ad33135f1 fix: YAML parsing error by escaping `|` in `title`
### Documentation updates
* 058a3c0987c27ca62a45f009e704caa9b37ae447 docs: Add link to article
* 3739b0bd8d18849af879a86dedf93060b171e78b docs: Describe how to use tools installed with Flatpak
* ab1b31ce5232296762a7cc25f8ee50cbffe45a55 docs: Add link to blog
